start() - Method in class engine.engine.EngineCore
Initialises all resources and classes:
- MouseManager
- KeyManager
- GraphicsEngine
- GameCore

Then starts game loop by calling EngineCore.startGameLoop()
start() - Method in class launcher.watchdog.EngineWatchdog
Starts the watchdog.

Enters a while loop, calling EngineWatchdog.update() repeatedly until an ExitReport is submitted to EngineWatchdog.submitExitReport(ExitReport), and EngineWatchdog.exitReport is no longer null.

The watchdog will then attempt to handle the ExitReport by calling EngineWatchdog.onExitReport(ExitReport).
startGameLoop() - Method in class engine.engine.EngineCore
Runs an infinite loop until the SHOULD_QUIT flag EngineCore.flagManager is true.

submitExitReport(ExitReport) - Static method in class launcher.watchdog.EngineWatchdog
Sets the EngineWatchdog.exitReport to the ExitReport passed in.

This causes the WATCHDOG_THREAD to break out of the while loop in EngineWatchdog.start(), to then handle the report accordingly.
